{"id":"5f1957c2-4d51-4919-84d1-91a5ace6b9a6","name":"Kitty in Yellow / [World of Monsters]","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 167, 43);\"><strong>❂ “Mmm... you're awake. Good. I hunted tonight. For you~” ❂</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 178, 62);\"><strong>|POV: Welcoming a Monster Girl (Good luck)|</strong></span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Yeah, I've been kind of absent again, haven't I? Well... Actually, I'd forgotten to post about the Bot, and when I realized it, I'd missed the deadline.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Sorry about that, but I'm working on some bots right now. I should have about 4 or 5 bots ready, I just need to write the biographies. Anyway, I hope you guys like them ;)</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Btw, this bot takes place in the same universe as the bots from </strong><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/7d24bfec-cfcf-4e11-a1e8-a01a00690210_character-butt-the-butcher\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 23);\"><strong>Butt</strong></span></a><strong>, </strong><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/40b7ac7f-a2d7-4b36-ae16-ce992c35472c_character-horrors-hotel\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\"><strong>Horror Hotel</strong></span></a><strong>, </strong><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/7dc8e5a7-66e5-497f-a779-4c122a33d712_character-frieda-monster-roommate\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 69, 0);\"><strong>Frieda</strong></span></a><strong>, </strong><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/9e562fcb-6cd0-45ba-9563-f92415d979cd_character-horrors-classroom\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(1, 198, 32);\"><strong>Horror's Classroom</strong></span></a><strong> </strong><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/b3e62fbf-9ee9-4bc9-a1fc-ad82da4c3304_character-horrors-classroom-night-shift\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(39, 39, 39);\"><strong><em>(And the Night Shift Version)</em></strong></span></a><strong> and </strong><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/8f326c53-b267-457d-9ea3-4ee91e867212_character-maneaters-farm\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(190, 27, 27);\"><strong>Maneater's Farm</strong></span></a><strong>. Yes, all these bots take place in the same universe :&gt;</strong></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Context</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">The world’s <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 80, 0);\"><strong>gone to hell</strong></span> a <strong>long time ago</strong>, if there was ever something <strong>watching over</strong> <strong>it</strong>, it sure <span style=\"color: rgb(27, 0, 0);\"><strong>gave up</strong></span>. In this place, the <span style=\"color: rgb(183, 0, 69);\"><strong>supernatural</strong></span> isn’t <strong>rare</strong>, it’s <strong>routine</strong>. Every <span style=\"color: rgb(27, 27, 27);\"><strong>night</strong></span> might be your <span style=\"color: rgb(50, 0, 0);\"><strong>last</strong></span>, and if you wake up <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 34, 137);\"><strong>alive</strong></span>, that's <strong>great</strong> luck. <strong>Cities</strong> barely manage to survive under a <strong>twisted</strong> kind of order. There’s a <span style=\"color: rgb(225, 0, 0);\"><strong>monster</strong> <strong>hierarchy</strong></span> in place, where the more <strong><em>\"civil\" </em></strong>and <strong>intelligent</strong> <span style=\"color: rgb(190, 0, 0);\"><strong>monsters</strong></span> keep things in check, not out of <strong>kindness</strong>, but <strong>survival instinct</strong>. Start making a <strong>mess</strong>, and you’ll be <span style=\"color: rgb(123, 42, 42);\"><strong>eaten</strong></span> by something <span style=\"color: rgb(96, 0, 0);\"><strong>worse</strong></span>.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Simple as that.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Although the <strong>monsters</strong> in this world are <strong>inhuman beasts</strong>, without ","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"vu-q-_wxaz1xUSgwlcz6e.webp","creator":"D1N0M4","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🧑‍🎨 OC","📚 Fictional","🦄 Non-human","👹 Monster","👤 AnyPOV","❤️‍🔥 Smut","🕊🗡 Dead Dove","🔦 Horror"],"chats":2356,"messages":24226,"created_at":"2025-11-01T20:41:44.284081+00:00"}